Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:28.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない夢を　君と君と　いつか　叶えられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:35.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなれる　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:47.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,それはPreviousもなく出会う奇跡 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:52.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,素顔を隠しながら　守るよ　もうひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:58.05,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってるんだずっと　その孤独を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:03.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah...　恐れないで　迷わないで　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:08.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する　必ず迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,届かない　明日は　高く高く　果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:20.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目の前にあるReal　願いこの空に消えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:26.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない　夢を　君が君が　いつか　ヒカリ望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:31.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとたどり着く　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:37.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君を　君を　君を　守りたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:41.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll Be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:28.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果將來能和你一起實現那永恆的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:35.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能夠變強 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:47.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有預告的奇跡邂逅 是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:52.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具守護你 再也不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:58.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直明白你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:03.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..不要害怕 不要疑惑 做你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:08.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證 一定會去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法觸及的明天 高高在上無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:20.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的現實讓願望消散在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:26.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在永恆的夢中期盼光明來臨的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:31.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會到達那裏 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:37.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:41.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我將與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:16.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでもキミの夢も明日(あす)も未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:22.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなるよ Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:35.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ちよダッシュして　どんなピンチも追い越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:41.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを(きっと)すぐに(Soon you feel)もう安心だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:46.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイマイ弱いハート　限界超えの勇気は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:52.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも(今も)キミの(信号)キャッチ I am ready！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:56.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰よりキミが大事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,熱くなってく　さあこの心で戦える！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミの夢も明日(あす)も未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:14.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,この手で絶対守るから　誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:18.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな涙も拭いてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:24.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっかしいな　でも笑顔でまた困らせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:27.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　まだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:30.02,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,小さな勇者は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:32.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　もっともっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:37.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなる Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:16.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠守護你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:22.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會變得更強大 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:35.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,讓心情馳騁起來 超越各種危機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:41.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會馬上就讓你覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:46.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,曖昧弱小的心需要超越極限的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:52.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都能捕捉到你的信號 我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:56.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為比誰都在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情不斷高漲 來吧 用這個心情去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:14.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓一定用這雙手來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:18.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你拭去所有的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:24.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看著好擔心啊 但是你的笑容又讓人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:27.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:30.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:32.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 要變得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:37.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,更強更強 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你溜掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次非逮到你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點的說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情報是正確的 那孩子..去了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心 真緒小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潔白的假面是正義的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從天涯海角來拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒 拜託稍微小聲一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「KnightLancer之歌」就必須大聲唱出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒名正言順地留在了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.97,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,..來幫助你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.23,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒的父親也幫她辦了手續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的她終於能上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一所名為森羅學園的..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包含了初等部 中等部 高等部的綜合學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒進入了它的初等部就讀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我則進入了高等部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲也一樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有回到宅邸裏的羽花小姐..白姬也..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？白姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬也想去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你們去太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶上面具的話白姬也不會露陷的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像KnightLancer一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 白姬 你冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:01.99,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.45,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子是有事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰去叫一下警察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 應該叫消防局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找點能讓她抓住的東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他帶著面具哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是戴著白色假面的正義英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴假面的..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您沒有受傷吧？女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer 好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明只是想過普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..這騎士道體質啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是KnightLancer麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午是什麼課啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也被你騙過一次的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這次是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥..我沒注意到有人啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..我被搞糊塗了..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？冴同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君 啊 這是..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 普通的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的學園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裏有台階
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不會這樣的..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人不會這樣做的..對我這麼親切..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還用「冴」來稱呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且花房君 對其他女生也都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子..有點..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的..一般情況下..不會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 十分對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..又做了什麼不同尋常的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我只是覺得花房君真是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟長年都在外國呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:07:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的身體接觸在國外很正常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說國外 其實是騎士之島罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們這真的有怪人出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那個變態一樣的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說今天早上那傢伙在上學的路上出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把面具戴在臉上什麼的 絕對很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會做出那種..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學她..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我剛到這個城市時 戴著面具所幫助過的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到我們會成為同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然啊..不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了？露出這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這位是我房東家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫鬼堂院真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫五十嵐冴 是花房君的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 葉太郎就拜託你了哦 冴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學 果然是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身為KnightLancer和騎士的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不能讓她知道才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 一整天談論的都是KnightLancer的話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 真緒小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上它被依子小姐帶回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬不能一起去上學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是真緒的請求..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為發生了一件有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬 白姬也能去學校了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的事是指什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽花她..沒有做錯任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在電話裏想聽你的聲音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐成了那傢伙的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙把老大打成這樣 姐姐還要當他同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希露比亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見你啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好久沒見到你了 所以一激動就..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興你能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希露比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 羽炎 過得好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快幫老大報仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希露比亞也是騎士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那種傢伙..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說爸爸是在堂堂正正的對決中落敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他並沒有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼做兒女的我們也該接受這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大沒有輸..老大他..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由俺來報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由俺來..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的..我的手指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？糟..糟了啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為..為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強大的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毀「幫」的..強大的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成這傢伙..目標是老大？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強大的日本人..他的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.07,0:00:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君 謝謝你的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏 一點小事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐 她說有什麼有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底在盤算什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希露比亞 你也在森羅學園上學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識她？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說是兒時玩伴還是什麼呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士的前輩..沒法跟她這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君 為了保護我做了那麼厲害的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？走是指..喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..你要把花房君帶去哪？喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個建築物是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該已經閒置很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲..羽花小姐..還有依子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連白姬也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家..為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 冴也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你很久了哦 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像不像KnightLancer？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會出現那個名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是乃麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是3年級的陽月乃麗學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 既然所有人都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就開始騎士部的活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士部？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是吧 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,培養英雄的社團？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這就是騎士部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃麗啊 去過很多國家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並進行了很多關於英雄的學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明聽說陽月乃麗學姐..是學園創立以來的大才女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作為學園的代表一直在外留學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你所學習的 就是英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我英雄的美妙之處的人就是乃麗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是乃麗去外國之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天你也在這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經很晚了哦 不回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想回..沒有母親在的家..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裏只有我一人 父親也從不回來..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人的家..我受夠了..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄就算孤身一人也很堅強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便孤軍奮戰也絕不畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對強大的敵人也絕不逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護重要的人而奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護而戰..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人也很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能變得像英雄一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護別人 就算孤身一人還是很堅強？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後 我就決定要以成為英雄為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要變得強大 為了不讓遠在天國的母親擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲真是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因為夢想成為英雄而變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也希望葉太郎能夠變強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊來啊 不好好努力可沒法成為英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生的狀態如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那個..差不多到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還遠遠沒有到極限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話和島上的生活完全沒有兩樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的學園生活啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚴格地鍛煉他吧 依子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 身為騎士部顧問我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..花房君可能不適合這種事吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能以不適合為理由就放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..花房君他那麼溫柔善良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼粗暴的事情實在是..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是強大的話並不能稱為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 要表現出符合英雄之名的行為舉止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難..難不成是指..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君不會做那種變態的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻 接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 啾一個~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在說什麼啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強大的日本人..他的名字是..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼還在這裏玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來陪我聊兩句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話 前途難料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和乃麗是在美國認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她說了KnightLancer的事之後 她非常感興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..金剛寺先生的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不是來報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是來找個人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有很多事想說 不過我現在需要人手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了向摧毀組織的男人報仇 你也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話你無故消失的事情就不予追究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強大的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 你也想一雪前恥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多人欺負一位女士..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此過分之事 我不能袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的面具小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金剛寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這是金剛寺先生的..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折斷你的槍的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把它重新製作成了適合你的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無需多言 為了女士而戰 這是..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身為我的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer 強大的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳的..爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:09.96,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收看槍與假面舞會的各位觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.59,0:23:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請向可愛的白姬投出你神聖的一票
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你在幹什麼啊？白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選舉活動啊 白姬立志要成為第一個白馬大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒真是頭一回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為大總統之後 第一件事就是要判愛麗絲死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 不疼愛白姬的人也要死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太嚴厲了吧 這不是最差勁的獨裁國家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊 這是可愛的白姬所統治的美妙國度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很感謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得應該不會吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 下回的槍與假面舞會將換成白姬當選的實況轉播
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以當選為前提嗎！
